snippet.title: (Cancelled) Super Mario Story - First Look
snippet.description:
Super Mario Story is an unofficial mod of New Super Mario Bros. 2 that sees Mario venturing off far away from the Mushroom Kingdom, with new and original locations, fun and inventive level design, an original story, and so much more!

Join our Discord Server! https://discord.gg/Tfm6UGMU2k

Also huge shoutout to GrishHung for his amazing remix of VS Overworld theme. The trailer wouldn't be what it is without it!
